name: My Planet Storms
description:
The name of our planet is big moon . It’s in the Miner Galaxy .It’s between the planet Gold and the Platium planet.
The planet is very big. Usually has got 20ºC. The day lasts 48 h.
It has got many mountains. Every mountain has got a kingdom. The most famous kingdom is the moon kingdom. In the Esmerald kingdom there are one million inhabitants. The people of these planets are diamonds and they are all girls. They are born in the gold mountain.
